{"tid":1525700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣新名目及戰線-Decitizenize","createTime":"2019-09-01T02:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T03:22:50.000Z","uid":56453,"like":98,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"135c911a39e30e362a467a86977ad222fd4e4cf5","tid":1525700,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:24:58.000Z","msg":"大家應該都好清楚警察既散仔福利會同唔少建制議員公開地稱示威者為曱甴啦<br />\n最近亦有新聞話有白衫警察出memo叫啲下屬唔好再叫示威者做曱甴<br />\n<br />\n尋晚831，有警察被記者質疑佢地無差別攻擊市民，個警察就話嗰啲係示威者，唔係市民<br />\n此外，凌晨4點既press con個女警話地鐵內有暴力示威者喬裝市民<br />\n言下之意，即是將示威者同市民割裂？係兩個唔同既團體？係可以差別對待？<br />\n只要一個人(或被懷疑)參與過示威，佢就唔再係市民，佢就唔享有市民既權利？<br />\n咁唔怪知得啲警察咁中意虐待被捕人士，原來係唔當啲人係市民，因而剝奪佢地應有權利<br />\n理論上，就算係法庭判決過有罪既犯人，佢地都一概係市民<br />\n警察無視法制及道德操守要求，任意妄為<br />\nDecitizenize加上Dehumanize，令到被捕人士受到不人道及不適當對待<br />\n<br />\n請大家一定要spread開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8aa10e2b57869300700cbf20acef80e0554be18","tid":1525700,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:25:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c6d649a9633f30b3e0dc1a7e87c6d5c150781440","tid":1525700,"uid":242083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:25:21.000Z","msg":"831恐襲同721恐襲冇分別<br />\n我正式宣佈香港警察係有牌黑社會兼恐怖分子<br />\n<br />\nYouTube 真係勁多五毛，你哋唔入去幫手comment下？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeYzNsiOy00o&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=6ecfee37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r2_c1Lc6MiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr2_c1Lc6MiU&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=4d172ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r2_c1Lc6MiU</a>"},{"pid":"94c84bdd7cb9a1b0b2ab9ff5aadc7c513fc9e9e6","tid":1525700,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"960e8